<p class="ayah 68-35" id="35" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَفَنَجْعَلُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then will We treat</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمُسْلِمِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Muslims</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَٱلْمُجْرِمِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">like the criminals?</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>35<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
