<p class="ayah 68-37" id="37" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) for you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كِتَـٰبٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a book</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِيهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">wherein</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَدْرُسُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you learn,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>37<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
